    "body": "FWIW, `fDnTOc` is the [default cleanup](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/blob/develop/libsolidity/interface/OptimiserSettings.h#L62) steps which you configure via the [cleanup sequence delimiter `:`](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/latest/internals/optimizer.html#selecting-optimizations). If not set, the default of `fDnTOc` is applied (as in your example). You should try to set `optimizerSteps = 'u:'`, i.e. use an empty entry for the default cleanup sequence.",
